presentation.title: Hello, I'm Maria Eduarda!
presentation.content: Graduated in Computer Science from the Federal University of Campina Grande (UFCG), I am passionate about my field. During my undergraduate studies, I had the opportunity to engage in excellent research and development projects, which contributed to my growth as a developer and Software Engineer. Throughout this journey, I also became a great enthusiast of Data Science and Artificial Intelligence, particularly in the areas of Computer Perception and Computer Vision, which I have chosen to pursue in my academic life.
